Dialogue.text: Good morning, Sector 7! Today is the 1st day of Gnarl, just ten days before Overlord Aso will visit one very special podtown.

Dialogue330.text: All hail Overlord Aso. Who's a good overlord? You are!

Dialogue339.text: In other news, a new virus has been discovered in Sector 6 and travel has been restricted.
